    "description": {
      "value": "<div><em>Wondrous Item (requires attunement)</em></div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>While wearing this Amulet, you can use an action to name a location that you are familiar with on another plane of existence. Then make a DC 15 Intelligence check. On a successful check, you cast the <em>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.J6Jpw5XzB5aTeqnz]{Plane Shift}</em> spell. On a failure, you and each creature and object within 15 feet of you travel to a random destination. Roll a d100. On a 1-60, you travel to a random location on the plane you named. On a 61-100, you travel to a randomly determined plane of existence.</div>",
